33331678365682641.Text: Eydis Fire-Eye told me to talk to Alof the Easterner at his farm northeast of Pelagiad and just north of the Arvel Plantation. Alof saw some Orcs at a Daedric ruin nearby.

53567799791415.Text: Eydis Fire-Eye told me to get rid of some orcs near Alof's Farm, northeast of Pelagiad. Alof was our source of information on this, and he's dead. I'm to search nearby until I find the right orcs. They may be hiding in some ruins.

50942449568778191.Text: Alof the Easterner said the Orcs come from Ashunartes which is northeast of here and just west of an old Dunmer stronghold. Alof thinks the rest of the Orcs will leave if I kill their leader, a Barbarian by the name of Burub gra-Bamog.

3075114533168318029.Text: Alof thanked me for getting rid of the Orcs at Ashunartes. I should report back to Eydis Fire-Eye.

289519483102661641.Text: Eydis Fire-Eye gave me 500 gold for the Duke's contract.

1009099651390419173.Text: Fighters Guild: Alof and the Orcs
